{"tid":2499464,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"亞洲匯豐享有高度自治 消息指王冬勝對匯豐總部調遷表達不滿","createTime":"2021-04-22T02:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T03:34:49.000Z","uid":362199,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a4e912c159c8cb1248ff4a0cb892d9bfabb4a192","tid":2499464,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1092870&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1092870%26newssource%3DHK6&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=6bd4fb32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1092870&amp;newssource=HK6</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社》引述消息人士指，滙豐控股(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=a292454e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)擬調遷四名高層往亞洲的決定引來多方不滿，先是大中華區的高級管理層恐官僚將令集團於亞洲的發展步伐放慢，亦有消息人士指過往一直在亞洲區享有高度自主的地區主管王冬勝對調遷成本表達不滿。報道並引述其中一位調遷高層、投資銀行部門聯席主管Greg Guyett曾於電話會議上提及亞洲地區的管理差勁(poor management)。<br />\n數據<br />\n匯豐控股累積表現<br />\n年初至今\t +10.55%<br />\n -2.07%\t1個月<br />\n銀行平均累積表現<br />\n年初至今\t +4.16%<br />\n1個月\t +0.39%<br />\n更新於 2021/04/22 09:44<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，部份員工受到高層調遷往亞洲的決定感鼓舞。滙控發言人拒就報道作出評論。(vi/da)"},{"pid":"ea8c048eba9fa15ffb73eb7b308b57adbe64a952","tid":2499464,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e930c8f713f52ca683a60586414d2ec36de6d8e3","tid":2499464,"uid":522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"亦有消息人士指過往一直在亞洲區享有高度自主的地區主管王冬勝對調遷成本表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n高度自主唔代表完全自主，學中共玩法姐"},{"pid